Title: What Have You Done?
Writer: Pendleton Ward (created by), Merriwether Williams (story by), Timothy McKeon (story by), Elizabeth Ito, Adam Muto
Actors: Jeremy Shada, John DiMaggio, Tom Kenny, Hynden Walch
Plot: After being told to arrest the Ice King, Finn and Jake face an ethical quandary when they realize the villain has not actually committed any recent crimes.
